cms.documentlocalization.DocumentName: Changeable Paper Filters for Vacuum Pot
cms.documentlocalization.DocumentSKUDescription:
Throw away the impractical cotton filter that you got with your Vacuum Pot Hario TCA-2 and replace it with these easy-to-use paper filters.

No need for cleaning, just use one and throw it away. The quickest and cleanest way to make a cup of coffee. Paper filters allow the coffee to flow through the filter. Additionally, they trap the coffee grounds inside the filter.
